OL,3,CThree due in court over alleged arson
OL,4,Cattack on Jewish community ambulances
OL,6,FThree males are due in court after
OL,7,Ffour Jewish community ambulances were
OL,8,Ftargeted in an alleged arson attack in
OL,9,Fnorth-west London.
OL,11,FFour ambulances from Hatzola, a
OL,12,Fvolunteer-led ambulance service
OL,13,Foperating in the Golders Green area of
OL,14,Fnorth-west London, were set on fire in
OL,15,Fthe early hours of March 23, causing
OL,16,Fgas canisters stored in the vehicles
OL,17,Fto explode.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/3
