OL,3,CThree due in court over alleged arson
OL,4,Cattack on Jewish community ambulances
OL,6,FHamza Iqbal, 20, and Rehan Khan, 19,
OL,7,Fboth British nationals from Leyton,
OL,8,Fand a 17-year-old boy, a dual British
OL,9,Fand Pakistani national from
OL,10,FWalthamstow, have been charged with
OL,11,Farson being reckless as to whether
OL,12,Flife would be endangered.
OL,14,FThe accused, who were arrested as part
OL,15,Fof a Counter Terrorism Policing (CTP)
OL,16,Finvestigation, are set to appear at
OL,17,FWestminster Magistrates' Court on
OL,18,FSaturday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/3
