OL,3,CThree due in court over alleged arson
OL,4,Cattack on Jewish community ambulances
OL,6,FTwo other men aged 45 and 47 who were
OL,7,Farrested last week, and are also
OL,8,FBritish, were released on bail until
OL,9,Flate April.
OL,11,FThe case is not being treated as
OL,12,Fterrorism but CTP said due to "the
OL,13,Fcircumstances of the incident" the
OL,14,Finvestigation is being led by its
OL,15,Fdetectives.
